<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad Schwarzenberger</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Peter N., ehemals Lochhüter zu Nürnberg, Unkenntnis wegen übler Nachrede geäußert hat.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_391" id="195r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_391_r1l1"><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>Swarcʒemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_391_line_1576481412401_1319"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> beuor / <expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> / Als du vns <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_391_r1l4">haſt / von des <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der vnſer <expan>Lochhüt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_391_r1l6">Darvmb 
<add><ab facs="#facs_391_r1l5"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> wir Jn <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> deinen <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> beſant / vnd Jn deinen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_391_r1l7">brief hören laſſen vnd dar auf cʒe rede geſacʒt / . Vnd er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_391_r1l8">hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / Er hab <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> rede <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dir nicht getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_391_r1l9">vnd wer dir das <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Jm geſagt hab / der tü Jm daran </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_391_r1l10">vngütlıch / vnd wöll auch dafür ſein recht <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> tün / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_391_r1l12">VVilt du nu 
<add><ab facs="#facs_391_r1l11">wenn <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim ıſt </ab></add> ſo macht du wol etwen her ſchıcken / <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_391_r1l13">deinen <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> dabeÿ ſeÿ / daʒ er das recht dafür tü / . Dann </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_391_r1l14">erfüren vvir / daʒ er ſölıch rede <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dir tet / So <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_391_r1l15">Jn darvmb vngeſtrafft nicht laſſen / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_391" id="195r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Swarczemberg<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> bevor. <expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, als du uns
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hast von des
                            <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der unser <expan>lochhüt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, darumb
                                <add><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add> wir in
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> deinen <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> besant
                        und in deinen brief hören lassen und darauf cze rede gesaczt; und er hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, er hab
                            <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> rede <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dir
                        nicht getan und, wer dir das <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> im gesagt hab, der
                        tü im daran ungütlich und wöll auch dafür sein recht
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> tün. Wilt du nu, <add>wenn
                                    <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim ist</add>, so macht du wol etwen
                        her schicken, <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> deinen <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> dabey sey,
                        daz er das recht dafür tü. Dann erfüren wir, daz er sölich rede
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dir tet, so
                            <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in darumb ungestrafft nicht
                        lassen.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
